// WORKING NAME: "Empowered Reach" (placeholder — needs naming pass)
// Ability: blood_boil
// Rarity: Rare
// Uniqueness: Exclusive
//
// Effect: Behavior hook "blood_boil_dnd_range".
//
// Hook behavior (Phase 6 — implemented in ability/hooks.rs::BloodBoilDndRange, registered in
// AbilityPlugin):
//   Reads PlayerZonePresence (zone/components.rs).
//   If presence.is_inside("death_and_decay"):
//     Doubles the "radius" param (Blood Boil's self_nova reads "radius") before the behavior
//     resolves (Pre hook) — Mechanics: "Blood boil has double range when cast inside D&D".
//   Otherwise: no effect.
//
// This demonstrates the zone-presence pattern without modifying D&D or the base
// blood_boil ability definition. The zone interaction is encoded entirely in this hook.
//
// Listed in blood_boil.ability.ron under hooks: [(Pre, "blood_boil_dnd_range")]. Deliberately NOT
// in blood_boil's talent_pool this phase, so the golden campaign can't offer/acquire it (keeping
// the master byte-identical); validated by tests/zone.rs instead.
(
    id: "blood_boil_dnd_range_rare",
    display_name: "Empowered Reach",
    ability_scope: Some("blood_boil"),
    rarity: Rare,
    uniqueness: Exclusive,
    effect: Behavior("blood_boil_dnd_range"),
)
